node_modules
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/build
# Exclude incremental build state — a stale tsbuildinfo copied into the image
# makes composite `tsc` skip emit (dist is excluded), breaking the image build.
**/*.tsbuildinfo
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
**/coverage
**/*.log
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/test
**/tests
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.js
docs
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE
infra/certs
infra/backups
infra/data
.dockerignore
.gitignore
.editorconfig
.nvmrc
.prettierrc
.prettierignore
*.md
